<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span style="color:#008000">(٧)</span> بَابُ الشِّرْكِ فِي الْعِبَادَةِ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span style="color:#006d98">س ٤٧:</span> مَا مَعْنَى الشِّرْكِ فِي الْعِبَادَةِ؟ وَمَا هِيَ أَقْسَامُهُ؟<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span style="color:#006d98">الشِّرْكُ هُوَ:</span> اتِّخَاذُ شَرِيكٍ مَعَ اللهِ تَعَالَى فِي الْعِبَادَةِ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span style="color:#006d98">وَهُوَ قِسْمَانِ:</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>١ - الشِّرْكُ الْأَكْبَرُ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>٢ - الشِّرْكُ الْأَصْغَرُ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>* * *<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span style="color:#006d98">س ٤٨:</span> مَا الشِّرْكُ الْأَكْبَرُ؟<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span style="color:#006d98">الشِّرْكُ الْأَكْبَرُ هُوَ:</span> صَرْفُ شَيْءٍ مِنْ أَنْوَاعِ الْعِبَادَةِ لِغَيْرِ اللهِ تَعَالَى.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>* * *<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span style="color:#006d98">س ٤٩:</span> اذْكُرْ أَمْثِلَةً عَلَى الشِّرْكِ الْأَكْبَرِ؟<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>الشِّرْكُ الْأَكْبَرُ لَهُ أَمْثِلَةٌ،<span style="color:#006d98"> فَمِنْ ذَلِكَ:</span><a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>الاسْتِغَاثَةُ بِالْمَوْتَى، وَالذَّبْحُ لِغَيْرِ اللهِ -مِنَ الْقُبُورِ أَوِ الْجِنِّ أَوِ الشَّيَاطِينِ-،<span style="color:#006d98"> وَمِنْ ذَلِكَ أَيضًا:</span> طَلَبُ المَدَدِ مِنَ الْأَوْلِيَاءِ وَالصَّالِحِينَ فِيمَا لَا يَقْدِرُ عَلَيْهِ إِلَّا اللهُ مِنْ قَضَاءِ الْحَاجَاتِ، أَوْ تَفْرِيجِ الْكُرُبَاتِ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>